Package: reptimod
Title: Reptile Integrated Distribution Modelling Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Rebecca", family = "Turner", email= "bectur@ceh.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5159-8266")),
  person(given  = "Nick", family = "Isaac", role  = "aut"),
  person(given  = "Francesca", family = "Mancini", role = "aut"))
Description: Tools to build, fit and evaluate integrated single- and multi-season occupancy models for UK reptiles using Nimble. Functions
 support data preprocessing, model configuration, run workflows, and visualise outputs (maps, diagnostics, calibration plots).
URL: https://github.com/becky-turner/reptimod
BugReports: https://github.com/becky-turner/reptimod/issues
